content:
Map Outputs to Voice Call Summary Fields

To store generated Summary, Issue, and Resolution outputs, map these outputs to fields of the VoiceCall object or one of its related objects. This must be done before activating work summaries for the service channel.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS:
Edit on VoiceCall OR Modify All Data

From Setup, enter Einstein Work Summaries, then select it. Click the Voice Calls tab and Edit. Select the Salesforce object field where you want to map each output. Fields with Text Area and Text Area (Long) data types appear in the picklist.

TIP: To map a field, have field-level security access on the field. Changing field mappings after setup is not recommended as this may cause missing content on summaries pages.
title: Configuring Einstein Work Summaries in Service Cloud
